divs: Sighting DetailsThis event took place about 4 or 5 times around 7pm. No sound. Straight line from East to West about 5,000 ft above ground. On one occasion the UFO was intercepted by an F4 Phantom Jet from the Ramey Airforce Base from Aguadilla, PR.
